# Component Directory Structure

## Generic Components

### Shared Components
- Generic components should be in `web-common/src/components`
- These are reusable components that can be used across multiple applications (web-admin, web-local)
- Examples: `Button.svelte`, `Modal.svelte`, `DataTable.svelte`, `FormField.svelte`

### Component Organization in web-common
```
web-common/src/components/
├── ui/                    # Basic UI components (buttons, inputs, etc.)
├── layout/               # Layout components (headers, footers, etc.)
├── data/                 # Data display components (tables, charts, etc.)
├── forms/                # Form-related components
└── feedback/             # Feedback components (alerts, notifications, etc.)
```